OL,3,CMan and company face multiple charges
OL,4,Cfor dumping tonnes of waste on rural
OL,5,Croad
OL,7,FA man and a company face multiple
OL,8,Fcharges after more than 27 tonnes of
OL,9,Frubbish was dumped on a road near
OL,10,FLichfield.
OL,12,FThe huge pile of industrial waste was
OL,13,Fdumped on Watery Lane in the early
OL,14,Fhours of January 20 - and it cost
OL,15,Ftaxpayers almost #10,000 to remove and
OL,16,Fdispose of it.
OL,18,FThe fly-tipping incident saw some
OL,19,Flocals wake up to find their only
OL,20,Froute to and from their homes
OL,21,Fcompletely blocked.
