OL,3,CMan and company face multiple charges
OL,4,Cfor dumping tonnes of waste on rural
OL,5,Croad
OL,7,FLichfield District Council said a man
OL,8,Ffrom Uttoxeter now faces multiple
OL,9,Fcharges, including depositing waste,
OL,10,Fendangering road users, dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving, breaching HGV drivers' hours
OL,12,Fregulations and obstructing the
OL,13,Fhighway.
OL,15,FA company based near Stafford has also
OL,16,Fbeen charged with depositing the waste
OL,17,Fand obstructing the highway.
OL,19,FBoth have been scheduled to appear at
OL,20,FCannock Magistrates' Court at 10am on
OL,21,FTuesday 1 July.
