OL,3,CMan and company face multiple charges
OL,4,Cfor dumping tonnes of waste on rural
OL,5,Croad
OL,7,FCouncillor Doug Pullen, the leader of
OL,8,FLichfield District Council, said:
OL,9,F"This was an appalling act of
OL,10,Fenvironmental crime.
OL,12,F"Local people woke up to find their
OL,13,Fonly route to and from their homes
OL,14,Fcompletely blocked, and the cost to
OL,15,Fthe taxpayer of removing and disposing
OL,16,Fof the waste was nearly #10,000.
OL,18,F"Thanks to the swift action of our
OL,19,Fenvironmental health officers,
OL,20,Fsuspects were quickly identified,
OL,21,Fleading to these charges."
