OL,7,FCllr Pullen continued: "We take a zero-
OL,8,Ftolerance approach to fly-tipping,
OL,9,Fbecause that's what our communities
OL,10,Frightly expect.
OL,12,F"This case is about more than
OL,13,Fprosecution. It's about protecting our
OL,14,Fenvironment, supporting law-abiding
OL,15,Fbusinesses, safeguarding local
OL,16,Fpeople`and sending a strong message
OL,17,Fthat illegal dumping will not be
OL,18,Ftolerated."
